entries.femaleVariant: Haha, with scratch like ours? In Little China? Choom, you can buy anything and anyone you want.
We pull out our wallets, their scopsucker eyes'll pop right outta their heads. C'mon, let's go, have a little fun.
But it's a... a rough neighborhood.
Helloooo. We got eddies. People can't touch us. Bullets can't hit us. We do whatever, whoever we feel like.
Well, yeah. But we could do that here.
Choom, grow some balls. How'd you get where you are now? Who gave you that suit? That car? Who's payin' your bills?
You're damn right. That's why you're goin' with me to Little China. Lemme teach you how to be a real ganic son-of-a-bitch.
